    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>《LUSTRA：拉琪亚的传说》是一款剧情丰富的角色扮演游戏，它融合了实时施法、探索和聚落建设元素，故事发生在一个破碎的浮空岛屿领域，古老的魔法与神秘在此交织。</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扮演拉琪亚，一位受周围世界塑造的年轻法师，她将在这片悬浮于毁灭与复兴之间的土地上，学会领导、成长并掌控自己的道路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lustra 邀请玩家通过多重视角审视世界，反思道德、共情与责任，并在此过程中不仅塑造魔法世界的结局，更塑造拉琪亚的人格成长。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301430/extras/1cd52418ff0967ce9b3c2c321d0756b4.poster.avif?t=1762268333\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301430/extras/1cd52418ff0967ce9b3c2c321d0756b4.webm?t=1762268333\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301430/extras/1cd52418ff0967ce9b3c2c321d0756b4.mp4?t=1762268333\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当她的妹妹无影无踪地消失后，拉琪亚踏上了穿越这个由魔法与记忆塑造的破碎世界的旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着旅程的展开，她将面临各种没有简单答案的情境——从挑战她信念的对话，到考验她优先事项的冲突，再到那些不仅塑造她个人未来，也影响着依赖她的人们命运的决定。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301430/extras/85d499c557ecc6a941ae3125459984c2.poster.avif?t=1762268333\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301430/extras/85d499c557ecc6a941ae3125459984c2.webm?t=1762268333\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301430/extras/85d499c557ecc6a941ae3125459984c2.mp4?t=1762268333\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过根据每个角色的独特才能分配任务、管理有限资源以及规划支持功能与发展的建筑布局，在天空中建立一个自给自足的村庄。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >密切关注社区士气，在这里，人们的情感福祉与他们的生产力同等重要。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301430/extras/1cd52418ff0967ce9b3c2c321d0756b4.poster.avif?t=1762268333\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301430/extras/1cd52418ff0967ce9b3c2c321d0756b4.webm?t=1762268333\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301430/extras/1cd52418ff0967ce9b3c2c321d0756b4.mp4?t=1762268333\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过实时、法术驱动的战斗来面对魔法威胁，这种战斗方式奖励时机把握、精准度和战场意识。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁强大的法术并升级拉琪亚的天赋，以塑造一种随她旅程一同成长的战斗风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301430/extras/a371d00dea995bace5d283e6174289bb.poster.avif?t=1762268333\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301430/extras/a371d00dea995bace5d283e6174289bb.webm?t=1762268333\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301430/extras/a371d00dea995bace5d283e6174289bb.mp4?t=1762268333\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在探索过程中发现隐藏在世界中的谜题与小游戏。有的简单，有的需要更多思考。它们都是旅途中静谧的片刻停留。</p>",
